{
  "global_image_tag": "ホラー",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_01",
      "start_sec": 0.0,
      "duration": 1.9,
      "text": "幽霊の気配は\n脳のバグだった",
      "type": "main_title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "001",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_02",
      "start_sec": 1.9,
      "duration": 2.95,
      "text": "“背後に誰かいる感覚”\nは脳の誤作動だった",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_03",
      "start_sec": 4.85,
      "duration": 2.55,
      "text": "パーキンソン病や幻覚症状のある患者に多い",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_04",
      "start_sec": 7.4,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "「誰かが背後にいる」感覚は、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_05",
      "start_sec": 9.44,
      "duration": 2.73,
      "text": "前頭頭頂ネットワークの錯調によるものと判明。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_06",
      "start_sec": 12.17,
      "duration": 2.68,
      "text": "自己と他者の境界を管理するこの回路が乱れると、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_07",
      "start_sec": 14.85,
      "duration": 3.68,
      "text": "“自分の動き”が“他者の存在”として誤認される。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_08",
      "start_sec": 18.53,
      "duration": 3.36,
      "text": "極限状態の脳は\n「他者の幻」を\n作りやすい",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_09",
      "start_sec": 21.89,
      "duration": 3.13,
      "text": "孤独・酸素欠乏・極度のストレス下では、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_10",
      "start_sec": 25.01,
      "duration": 2.79,
      "text": "脳が“擬似的な他者”を作り出すことがある。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_11",
      "start_sec": 27.81,
      "duration": 4.15,
      "text": "これは登山家・潜水士・宇宙飛行士に共通する現象で、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_12",
      "start_sec": 31.96,
      "duration": 2.4,
      "text": "「誰かがそばにいた」「導かれている気がした」",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_13",
      "start_sec": 34.36,
      "duration": 1.25,
      "text": "という感覚が頻発。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_14",
      "start_sec": 35.61,
      "duration": 2.6,
      "text": "脳が孤独に耐えるための緊急処理とみなされている。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "006",
      "emotion": "emotion: 悲しみ (sadness)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_15",
      "start_sec": 38.21,
      "duration": 3.64,
      "text": "“霊の気配”とされる\nゾクッとする感覚は\n体温調整反応",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "007",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_16",
      "start_sec": 41.85,
      "duration": 4.13,
      "text": "人が突然“寒気”や“鳥肌”を感じる現象は、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "007",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_17",
      "start_sec": 45.97,
      "duration": 2.68,
      "text": "不安や緊張時に起こる自律神経の反応であり、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "007",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_18",
      "start_sec": 48.65,
      "duration": 2.55,
      "text": "環境変化とは無関係に発生することがある。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_19",
      "start_sec": 51.2,
      "duration": 2.92,
      "text": "この生理現象が「何かが通った」などの",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_20",
      "start_sec": 54.12,
      "duration": 2.62,
      "text": "“気配の正体”として解釈されることがある。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 恐れ (fear)"
    }
  ]
}